data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Greenbriar, where modern elegance meets the charm of a rural type setting! SELLER IS OFFERING $6,000 TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS! This one-year-old home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and spaciousness in a truly peaceful location. With 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home provides ample space for your family's every need. The 18 x 18 tile floors, designer ceiling fans, and natural lighting add a touch of warm ambiance. The kitchen features a large island for culinary creations with bar seating.    Retreat to the owners suite with a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom. Three additional bedrooms provide flexibility for a home office, guest rooms, or a growing family. With a 2 garage and ample driveway parking, you'll have plenty of space for your vehicles.    Don't miss your chance to experience the best of both worlds – the comforts of a newer home, open-concept and the serenity of a rural type backdrop. This home is a "must-see" for those seeking modern living in a picturesque setting. Make this your forever home and move in asap!
